            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (9)

- Caches shared app icons by size so dialogs, About windows, and startup setup avoid repeated app icon lookup or decoding.
- Reuses status bar symbol images during menu refreshes instead of recreating them.
- Keeps the previous fast dialog and Finder right-click menu icon paths in place.
]]></description>
