            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (8)

- Fixes duplicated Finder right-click menu actions caused by multiple registered Finder extension copies from development and release builds.
- Avoids re-registering the Finder extension when opening or refreshing the right-click menu configuration window.
- Speeds up the first Finder right-click menu open by caching menu icons and mirrored Finder preferences.
]]></description>
